  "title": "PROJECT ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Responsibilities</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To supervise Drivers, Operators, General workers and maintenance of equipment at site.</li>\n  <li>Assist and support Project Manager in handling and monitoring smooth progress of project.</li>\n  <li>To ensure and carried out site work in accordance to construction programme safetly.</li>\n  <li>Must be familiar with all roads, drainage, sewers and all other infrastructure construction.</li>\n  <li>To carry out all site works issues and ad-hoc duties when instructed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>Requirements</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess Bachelor’s degree in Civil Engineering (RE Recognised)</li>\n  <li>Candidate to possess relevant certificates and Building Construction Supervisors Safety Course Certificate (BCSS)</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of working experience in the related field</li>\n  <li>Preferably with Class 3 Driving Licence</li>\n  <li>Good communication, self-initiative and interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>",
